column5: Heading for the weekend. Anyone have any info on the lake? Hear lake trout and bass but cant find much more info on it. Thanks
I think it has musky too.  S.
Would musky be open there as well starting this week-end? Maybe a later start?
Good luck launching I hear there is not much of a launch.
Taking a tin boat and small motor. Not too worried about launching, just curious to find what i will be fishing for.
It is a stocked, year round lake trout lake.  Beyond that, I dont know much other than its very deep for its size
A very interesting lake. Very clear and deep water.
There's a splake lake at one end of it you can hike into for a few casts. I've caught them in there before, but many years ago. Surprisingly decent numbers of musky in there.  S.
